videos.description: Egor Koulechov uses his dribble to create space and drills a step-back 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Florida's Koulechov goes behind the back for 3-pointer

videos.description: Jalen Hudson drains a 3-pointer and draws a foul for a chance at a 4-point play.
videos.headline: Florida's Hudson earns 4-point play

videos.description: Reid Travis dribbles his way to the basket where he gets deep position and throws down a powerful one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Stanford's Travis powers his way to the basket

videos.description: Chris Chiozza intercepts the pass and flips a no-look pass to Deaundrae Ballard, who lays it in and gets fouled.
videos.headline: Florida's tough defense leads to and-1

videos.description: Dontay Bassett grabs the offensive rebound and throws down a two-handed putback dunk.
videos.headline: Bassett throws down strong putback dunk
